    "Gamma spectroscopyAn independent experiment was conducted for γ spectroscopy to acquire complementary data and broaden the energy range of our analysis.",
    "Charge distributions were measured using four γ sources, 241 Am, 133 Ba, 109 Cd, and 137 Cs.",
    "These sources were placed near the crystal and aligned at its center during data taking.",
    "The energies of the γ rays and Xrays emitted from these sources, along with their exposure times, are listed in Table 2.",
    "Data without any sources was also collected over an extended period to obtain the background distributions before and after acquiring data with the sources."
